   <conbody>
      <p class="- topic/p ">When an agreement is first created, the agreement status is <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">In Request.</b> When a program is created from the agreement, its status is set to <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Draft.</b>
      </p>
      <p class="- topic/p ">After reviewing the agreement and program, Program analysts activate the agreement: this also activates any program associated to the agreement. Agreement and Program statuses are set to <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Activated.</b>
      </p>
